'''Gamorrean gauntlets''' were gloves created by the [[Gamorrean/Legends|Gamorrean]] race. They were heavy and clumsy, yet in unarmed combat allowed for powerful albeit less accurate blows. These gauntlets were believed to be impractical for combat with weapons.

==Appearances==
